Standard services
Responsible: The person/organization that carries out the task. He or she is accountable to the person ultimately responsible (Accountable);
Accountable: This person/organization is ultimately responsible for completing one or more project tasks. Therefore, accountability is given to the person ultimately responsible, and he or she approves or disapproves a task;
Consulted: This person/organization is asked for advice in advance. He or she must provide approval or input for a certain task in the project;
Informed: This person/organization is informed about the decisions in the progress of the process or project. Of course, this person cannot influence the result of the task.
